Class Summary

XNativeEQV A representation of logical variables.
XNativeField<T> A representation of a Field.T is a FieldDef or a MethodDef.
XNativeFormula<T> A representation of an atomic formula op(t1,..., tn).
XNativeLit A representation of a literal.
XNativeLocal<T> The representation of a local variable reference in the constraint system.
XNativeTerm Constraints constrain XTerms.
XNativeUQV An efficient representation of a universally quantified variable that is permitted to occur in multiple constraints.
XNativeVar  
XNot A representation of !c.
XPromise All nodes that occur in the graph maintained by a constraint must implement Promise.
